'''Laros Michael d'Encarnação Duarte''' ({{IPA|nl|ˈla.ɾos mɪ.ˈxa.əl|lang}} {{IPA|pt|dẽ.kɐɾ.nɐ.ˈsɐ̃w du.ˈaɾ.tɨ|lang}}; born 28 February 1997) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for Hungarian club [[Puskás Akadémia FC|Puskás Akadémia]].<ref name = "WF">{{Worldfootball.net|laros-duarte|new_id=pe373515}}</ref> Born in the Netherlands, he plays for the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].

==Club career==
Duarte made his debut for [[Eerste Divisie]] side [[Jong PSV]] in 2015. In the 2015–16 season, the footballer joined PSV. He used to play for [[Sparta Rotterdam]] from [[Rotterdam]] before he moved to Eindhoven.<ref>[https://www.psv.nl/psv/nieuws/artikel/jeugdspeler-duarte-tekent-bij-psv.htm Jeugdspeler Duarte tekent bij PSV] - PSV {{in lang|nl}}</ref>

On 31 August 2021, he signed a four-year contract with [[FC Groningen|Groningen]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FC Groningen|Groningen]]|url=https://www.fcgroningen.nl/nieuws/fc-groningen-bindt-laros-duarte/2|title=FC GRONINGEN BINDT LAROS DUARTE|date=31 August 2021|accessdate=30 September 2021|language=nl}}</ref>

On 23 August 2024, Duarte joined [[Puskás Akadémia FC|Puskás Akadémia]] in Hungary on a three-year contract.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Puskás Akadémia|url=https://puskasakademia.hu/?q=news/15242|title=Hollandiából érkezett erősítés|trans-title=Reinforcements arrived from the Netherlands|date=23 August 2024|access-date=23 August 2024|language=hu}}</ref>

==International career==
Born in the Netherlands, Duarte is of Cape Verdean descent. He was called up to the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]] for a set of [[2023 Africa Cup of Nations qualification]] matches in September 2023.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ilhas.li/aMo1|title=Cabo Verde enfrenta Togo na disputa pela liderança do grupo na qualificação para a CAN 2023|website=Expresso das Ilhas}}</ref>

