==Personal life==
He is the older brother of [[Deroy Duarte]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=CrioloSports|url=http://criolosports.com/index.php/criolos-no-estrangeiro/2878-criolos-no-estrangeiro-deroy-duarte-renova-com-sparta-rotterdam|title=Creoles Abroad: Deroy Duarte renews with Sparta Rotterdam|language=Portuguese|date=8 August 2017|access-date=20 September 2017|archive-date=13 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213222110/http://criolosports.com/index.php/criolos-no-estrangeiro/2878-criolos-no-estrangeiro-deroy-duarte-renova-com-sparta-rotterdam|url-status=dead}}</ref> Despite his last name, place of birth and country of descent; he is not related to fellow footballer [[Lerin Duarte]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nos.nl/artikel/2023040-psv-contracteert-duarte-van-sparta|title=PSV contracteert Duarte van Sparta}}</ref>

